title: January 26 - A.B Original (2016)
brief_description: January 26 was the hit single for hip hop duo A.B Original, which is made up of Briggs and Trials. In their debut album Reclaim Australia they frequently address issues facing Indigenous Australians.

constellations_other.name: Outlaws and the end
constellations_other.description: Tracing connections from Sweet Country to Australian westerns and resistance to white colonial narratives.
